  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix chopped tomatoes with aloe vera juice concentrate, coconut flour, ground flax seeds, sesame seeds, salt, black pepper, red chili flakes, and paprika. Stir until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture into a greased baking dish.",
    "Bake for 20-25 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool slightly before serving."
